title: LF 1/2 persons that want to travel from Netherlands to Spring Split Final (Sun 23 April) in Hamburg
body:
Hey all,
Two friends and me are going to visit the Spring Split finals in Hamburg on Sunday 24 April.

This time we will travel with a car from Wageningen to Hamburg.
Is anyone interested in joining the drive?

Some info about us:
we are three guys that have been playing league for several years and really like the atmosphere of game events (have been to see LoL in Berlin, Antwerpen and Rotterdam). We are in early 20's and IT-students.

David
